{"title":"安装Mysql","uid":"85b67fe6b30f1568e5071876ed7b54d4","slug":"安装MySQL","date":"2022-04-19T15:03:46.000Z","updated":"2022-04-20T09:32:23.158Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/安装MySQL.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/4.jpg","content":"<h3 id=\"安装MySQL\"><a href=\"#安装MySQL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装MySQL\"></a>安装MySQL</h3><p><strong>下载安装包：</strong><br>下载网址：<br><a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/\">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/81cc86510aa245848c28e03443f1a5ed.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2E4MDI5NzY=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h5><p><strong>添加环境变量</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>我的电脑-&gt;右键-&gt;属性-&gt;高级系统设置-&gt;<a href=\"https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F&spm=1001.2101.3001.7020\">环境变量</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>选择<code>Path</code>-&gt;编辑-&gt;新建，添加：你的mysql安装文件下的bin文件夹地址</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在安装目录下新建<code>my.ini</code>文件（文本文档）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>编辑<code>my.ini</code>文件，注意替换你自己电脑上的路径</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">[mysqld]\nbasedir &#x3D; D:\\environment\\mysql-5.7.31\\  &#x2F;&#x2F;把这两行路径改成自己的安装路径\ndatadir &#x3D; D:\\environment\\mysql-5.7.31\\data\\\nport &#x3D; 3306\nskip-grant-tables\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>启动cmd(用管理员身份)</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-mysql\" data-language=\"mysql\"><code class=\"language-mysql\">mysqld -install\nmysqld --initialize-insecure --user&#x3D;mysql<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>这步完成后，在文件夹里会生成一个<code>data</code>文件（如果没有就自己加一个）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>完成后会显示<code>MySQL 服务已经启动成功</code></p>\n<p>然后通过命令<code>mysql -u root -p</code>，进入mysql管理界面（密码为空）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">ALTER USER &#39;root&#39;@&#39;localhost&#39; IDENTIFIED BY &#39;111111&#39;;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>输入exit 退出</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"安装MySQL下载安装包：下载网址：https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/ 安装添加环境变量 我的电脑-&gt;右键-&gt;属性-&gt;高级系统设置-&gt;环境变量 选择Path-&gt;编辑-&gt;新建，添加：你的mysql安装文件下的bin文...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":635,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"-Mysql","slug":"Mysql","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Mysql.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"database","slug":"database","count":2,"path":"api/tags/database.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装MySQL</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"赫","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gss0.baidu.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/wh%3D600%2C800/sign=ba0d9106cfbf6c81f76224ee8c0e9d0d/b17eca8065380cd7b7acd783a244ad3459828129.jpg","link":"/","description":"life&&study","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Database note","uid":"a5ba081d42d4ddecbbc2164f3d549c44","slug":"Database Note","date":"2022-04-19T15:03:46.000Z","updated":"2022-04-20T09:27:26.398Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Database Note.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/3.jpg","text":"Database1.Overview of Data Models1.1.关系数据模型（Relational Model） A two-dimensional table called a relation Each relation has a name——关系名 Provid...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name"